{"tid":1363003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今朝日本スッキリ講述元朗事件","createTime":"2019-07-25T04:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T05:19:39.000Z","uid":13967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7503dbecce876f4edef85cf709ac26810e3fc1e5","tid":1363003,"uid":13967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:47:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/U0dD7MOWcVk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FU0dD7MOWcVk&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUd8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=264d0a66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/U0dD7MOWcVk</a><br />\n<br />\n3:20-19:10，一個叫石平的人評論元朗事件。片中所見，石平さん提到三合會和港共、中共政府的關係，但忽略了中聯辦（中共在港代表）、何君堯（西環契仔）、新界鄉事的角色（為何白衣恐襲選擇在元朗發生？）。石平提到中共政府幕後操縱沒有錯，不過嫌過份簡略了香港現實情況（例如背後的龐大土地利益）<br />\n<br />\n國際文宣，解釋官、商、警、鄉、黑、共的勾結關係和衍生的市民切身安全問題，我們還要加把勁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Fn8Qvs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Fn8Qvs.png&h=468647ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11aebb9594fe6fb773432cc94fdc48da2450f52c","tid":1363003,"uid":216800,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:48:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1iVuvP5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1iVuvP5.gif&h=9bc8a809&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e077e439652ccf037ec18c0fdac6488a25676f5b","tid":1363003,"uid":242851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11aebb9594fe6fb773432cc94fdc48da2450f52c","tid":1363003,"uid":216800,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:48:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1iVuvP5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1iVuvP5.gif&h=9bc8a809&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:55:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c04ced22188ebbd6ab6f96b0d240b48a05d01b7","tid":1363003,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote"